  <div class="game-box">
    <div class="timer">‚è≥ ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤: <span id="time">60</span> ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ</div>

    <h3>‡∏ä‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á</h3>
